beer.beer_description:
Take a long walk off our short Jetty. A creature of the deep is awaiting. Are you brave enough to take the plunge. At 8.8% and with all the depth of 8 American hops this IIPA will bite, but in a good way.

The IIPA recipe contains eight American hops, 8.8% ABV and 800kg of malt. With a sweet silky body that conceals the alcohol, balanced perfectly with a generous addition of eight hop varieties, the Infinite 8 layers beautiful citrus notes, dank and piney undertones with a big modern tropical fruit flavour.
